{"article_id":"YJvT6bniTOI30G7J","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Obama indicates a willingness","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to accept a short-term deal ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"a lawmaker says","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"GOP source :","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Republicans may have to accept a `` clean '' debt ceiling plan","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"A deadline looms","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to raise the debt ceiling","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"or face default for the first time","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"President Barack Obama indicated a willingness Wednesday to agree to a short-term deal","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"to raise the federal borrowing limit ,","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"if Republicans will accept it ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"a Democratic lawmaker told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"The president signaled more `` give '' to the idea of a six-week deal","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"to hike the debt ceiling","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"during a private White House meeting with House Democrats ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"said the lawmaker ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"who spoke on condition of anonymity .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"The revelation comes amid a stalemate","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that has Republicans trying to use spending and debt limit deadlines as leverage","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"to wring concessions from Obama and Democrats .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"The result of the political standoff has been a partial government shutdown","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that is in its second week","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and fears of a possible U.S. default on its debt","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"economists warn","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"could cause another recession .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"CNN has been reporting","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that senior House GOP sources are signaling openness to the idea of a short-term increase in the debt ceiling ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"as long as Democrats agree to negotiations","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"on how to reduce the debt and deficit during the time","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"the debt ceiling is increased .","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"Talking about a short-term solution ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"Obama told the group","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"`` if that 's what","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"( House Speaker John ) Boehner needs to climb out of the tree","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"that he 's stuck in ,","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"then that 's something","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"we should look at , ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"according to the lawmaker ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"who attended the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Charity helps Pentagon with benefits","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Charity helps Pentagon with benefits","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"02:22","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Defunding Obamacare a 'fool 's errand '","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":16},{"id":51,"text":"Defunding Obamacare a 'fool 's errand '","depth":16},{"id":52,"text":"05:45","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"Time running out for debt ceiling deal","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Time running out for debt ceiling deal","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"04:27","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"House gym remains open despite shutdown","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"House gym remains open","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"despite shutdown","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"03:14","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"The lawmaker left the White House meeting with a `` small measure of hope","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that this becomes an exit strategy . ''","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The president warned","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"if Republicans want to propose a short-term fix","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and Democrats say no ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"then the firm ground","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Democrats think","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"they 're standing on now","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"would soften .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Boehner and Republicans are demanding","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that Obama and Senate Democrats negotiate on deficit reduction steps","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that would be part of legislation","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"to reopen the government","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"and raise the limit on federal borrowing","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"needed to pay the bills .","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"Obama has refused to enter formal talks","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"until the shutdown ends","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"and the debt ceiling has been raised","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"to remove the threat of default .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"A senior House Republican told CNN","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"that GOP members may be willing to go for a short-term debt ceiling hike","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"-- lasting four to six weeks --","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"as long as the president agrees","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"that negotiations will occur during that time .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"However , no specifics were immediately available","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"about how such legislation would take shape","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"or how the talks would occur .","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"But Republican sources have also told CNN","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"the parameters of those talks have to be specific enough","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"to sell to their skeptical GOP members .","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"So what would Democrats be willing to talk about ?","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"The lawmaker said","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"House Democrats are open to hearing what Republicans have in mind with a short-term deal .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"The shutdown began","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"when Congress failed to pass a spending plan for the new fiscal year","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"that started October 1 .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Now another deadline looms","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"-- the need","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"to increase the federal borrowing limit by October 17","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"or risk a U.S. default .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Days of back-and-forth rhetoric and jibes between the leaders have brought no direct negotiations , but plenty of accusations and political spin .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"On Wednesday , GOP leaders appeared to shift their focus from efforts","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"to dismantle Obama 's signature health care reform , the initial driving force behind the shutdown ,","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"to securing spending cuts elsewhere .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"'Essential ' wife :","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Furlough may be better","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"MUST WATCH 'Essential ' wife :","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Furlough may be better","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"02:51","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Shutdown makes a cameo in Hollywood","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Shutdown makes a cameo in Hollywood","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"02:35","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"5-year-old distraught over shutdown","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"5-year-old distraught over shutdown","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"02:37","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"Boehner ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"who earlier this year told his GOP colleagues","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"that he was finished negotiating one on one with the president ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"has called for Obama to sit down for what he calls a `` conversation ''","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"on how to reopen the government","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"and prevent what would be the first-ever U.S. default as soon as next week .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"when Obama invited the entire House Republican caucus to the White House as part of a series of meetings with legislators ,","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"Boehner 's office responded","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"that only the GOP leadership and committee chairmen would attend the Thursday gathering .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"`` It is our hope that this will be a constructive meeting","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"and that the president finally recognizes","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Americans expect their leaders to be able to sit down and resolve their differences , ''","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"said a statement by a Boehner aide .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"Obama 's invitation was intended to demonstrate outreach to Republicans","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"just eight days from when the Treasury says","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Congress must increase the federal debt ceiling","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"or risk default .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"White House spokesman Jay Carney said","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"Obama was disappointed","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"that Boehner was limiting attendance at Thursday 's meeting to fewer than 20 of the more than 200 House Republicans .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"`` The president thought","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"it was important to talk directly with the members","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"who forced this economic crisis on the country ''","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"about the potential harmful impacts from the shutdown and a possible default ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"Carney said in a statement ,","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"repeating","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"that Obama `` will not pay the Republicans ransom","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"for doing their job . ''","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"Meanwhile , GOP leaders were distancing themselves from demands by tea party conservatives","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"to also make dismantling Obamacare a condition for agreement .","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"Republican Rep. Paul Ryan of Wisconsin , the House Budget Committee chairman","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"who was the party 's vice presidential nominee last year ,","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"argued in a Wall Street Journal op-ed","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"that Democrats and Republicans should focus on `` modest reforms to entitlement programs and the tax code . ''","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"`` Right now , we need to find common ground , ''","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"Ryan wrote in the column","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"posted online Tuesday night .","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"`` We need to open the federal government .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"We need to pay our bills today","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"-- and make sure","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"we can pay our bills tomorrow .","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"So let 's negotiate an agreement","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"to make modest reforms to entitlement programs and the tax code . ''","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"However , Ryan 's column never mentioned Obamacare ,","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"focusing instead on forced spending cuts to domestic and military programs , as well as reforms to Medicare .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"Ryan 's Obamacare omission appeared to anger conservatives ,","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"who took to Twitter in response .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"`` Much like White House press , Paul Ryan does n't mention Obamacare in WSJ oped , ''","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"tweeted Dan Holler , spokesman for the conservative group Heritage Action .","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"Perhaps in response to a conservative backlash , Boehner made a brief statement Wednesday on the House floor","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"that focused on the GOP message","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"that Obamacare was detrimental to the country .","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"He stopped short of linking it to any negotiations","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"on ending the shutdown","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"and raising the debt ceiling .","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"Boehner insists","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"that the government must reduce deficits ,","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"declaring","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"that Republicans wo n't raise the debt ceiling","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"without steps toward that goal .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"But a House GOP leadership source told CNN on Wednesday","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"that Obama 's rejection","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"of linking negotiations to raising the borrowing limit","depth":15},{"id":193,"text":"meant Republicans would likely be forced to agree to a `` clean '' debt ceiling limit proposal in exchange","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"for setting up talks on deficit reduction steps .","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"According to the source ,","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"the economic implications of a U.S. default `` scares people '' to make such a deal acceptable to enough House Republicans","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"in order to get negotiations started .","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"The source acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"Boehner may lack support from some or most of his GOP caucus ,","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"requiring Democratic votes","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"for the proposal to pass .","depth":13},{"id":202,"text":"Democratic Sen. Dick Durbin of Illinois told CNN","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"his side already was mulling over `` what we will discuss , what we will negotiate over , what things will be on the table . ''","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"Obama also met with the House Democratic caucus at the White House .","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"The GOP-led House passed a measure on Tuesday","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"to set up a special negotiating team","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"comprising members of both parties from the House and Senate ,","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"but Obama and Democrats rejected the concept as the latest Republican gimmick","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"to force talks","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"before raising the debt ceiling .","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"Meanwhile , Senate Democrats announced","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"they will propose a measure","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"to increase the debt ceiling beyond next year 's congressional elections","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"with no additional issues attached .","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"While many Republicans are certain to oppose it ,","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"Democratic leaders hope","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"increased pressure for Congress","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"to prevent a default next week","depth":14},{"id":219,"text":"will cause some GOP senators to vote for it .","depth":13},{"id":220,"text":"A GOP source told CNN on Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"that the White House was having corporate chief executives call Republican leaders .","depth":10},{"id":222,"text":"The business community has called for resolving the Washington stalemate","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"to avoid a default","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"that would spike interest rates","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"to impact the economy .","depth":13},{"id":226,"text":"Without a breakthrough ,","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"the shutdown would continue at a cost","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"estimated at up to $ 50 billion a month .","depth":12},{"id":229,"text":"Failure","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"to raise the debt ceiling by next week 's deadline","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"would leave the government unable to borrow money","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"to pay its bills","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"for the first time in its history .","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"All the partisan bickering","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"-- and lack of progress --","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"is taking its toll not just on furloughed workers , shuttered government facilities and programs ,","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"but also on Americans ' confidence in their government .","depth":10},{"id":238,"text":"In a national poll","depth":12},{"id":239,"text":"released Monday ,","depth":12},{"id":240,"text":"most respondents said","depth":11},{"id":241,"text":"the government shutdown was causing a crisis or major problems for the country .","depth":10},{"id":242,"text":"The CNN/ORC International survey indicated","depth":10},{"id":243,"text":"that slightly more people were angry at Republicans than Democrats or Obama for the shutdown ,","depth":11},{"id":244,"text":"though both sides took a hit .","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"According to the poll","depth":12},{"id":246,"text":"conducted over the weekend ,","depth":12},{"id":247,"text":"63 % of respondents said","depth":13},{"id":248,"text":"they were angry at the Republicans for the way","depth":14},{"id":249,"text":"they have handled the shutdown ,","depth":14},{"id":250,"text":"while 57 % expressed anger at Democrats and 53 % at Obama .","depth":12},{"id":251,"text":"`` It looks like there is more than enough blame","depth":13},{"id":252,"text":"to go around ,","depth":13},{"id":253,"text":"and both parties are being hurt by the shutdown , ''","depth":12},{"id":254,"text":"said CNN Polling Director Keating Holland .","depth":11},{"id":255,"text":"According to a new Gallup poll Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":256,"text":"the Republican party 's favorable rating dropped to 28 % , down 10 percentage points from September .","depth":11},{"id":257,"text":"The 43 % for Democrats was a 4-percentage-point drop from last month .","depth":11},{"id":258,"text":"Senate Democrats sought to keep up the pressure ,","depth":11},{"id":259,"text":"holding a rally on the Capitol steps on Wednesday","depth":12},{"id":260,"text":"to demonstrate their unified stance","depth":13},{"id":261,"text":"in calling for House Republicans to reopen the government and raise the debt ceiling .","depth":13},{"id":262,"text":"A CNN survey indicates","depth":12},{"id":263,"text":"enough Republicans in the House would join Democrats","depth":13},{"id":264,"text":"in voting for a Senate-passed spending plan","depth":14},{"id":265,"text":"to end the shutdown .","depth":14},{"id":266,"text":"All 200 Democrats and 19 Republicans support passing a continuing resolution with no additional legislative strings attached .","depth":15},{"id":267,"text":"With two vacancies in 435-member House , 217 votes are currently the minimum","depth":17},{"id":268,"text":"needed","depth":17},{"id":269,"text":"for the measure to win approval in the House .","depth":16},{"id":270,"text":"However , not enough Republicans are willing to join Democrats in a procedural move","depth":15},{"id":271,"text":"to force Boehner to hold a vote on the Senate plan .","depth":15},{"id":272,"text":"Boehner has said","depth":14},{"id":273,"text":"the measure would fail to pass in the House , a contention","depth":15},{"id":274,"text":"rejected by Obama and Democrats .","depth":15},{"id":275,"text":"The speaker has previously allowed measures to pass the House with mostly Democratic support ,","depth":14},{"id":276,"text":"which has weakened his leadership among conservatives .","depth":14},{"id":277,"text":"Doing so now could cost him his leadership post due to the conservative backlash","depth":15},{"id":278,"text":"in would likely unleash ,","depth":15},{"id":279,"text":"analysts believe .","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":559,"left":0,"right":558,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":558,"left":284,"right":557,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":283,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":283,"left":282,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":281,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":557,"left":387,"right":556,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":387,"left":376,"right":386,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":376,"left":318,"right":375,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":298,"right":317,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":295,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":286,"right":294,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":286,"left":6,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":289,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":288,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":287,"right":11,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":291,"right":292,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":290,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaborat